Output docs/demo-kindle.gif

Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Width 1920
Set Height 1080
Set FontSize 24
Set Framerate 60
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Padding 20
Set PlaybackSpeed 1

Sleep 500ms
Type "zlib kindle"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "mykindle@kindle.com"
Sleep 1s
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "sender@gmail.com"
Sleep 1s
Enter
Sleep 1s

Enter
Sleep 1s

Enter
Sleep 10s
